{"tid":1009221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長賭係咪真係必輸 有冇見過贏","createTime":"2019-02-05T04:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T10:56:26.000Z","uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92f688e2caaf6c1f7eaece4be1b80d4bfc0ebf61","tid":1009221,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380f0cbf5bbfa0508b69eed0d17842fbf05ed408","tid":1009221,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"有fd 一學賭波就贏到成皮，之後繼續就開始係咁豬，因為越買越多。<br />\n<br />\n後尾唔知佢賭乜贏左成30幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就無見過佢賭過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我估世界上應該好撚多依d人靠賭博賺第一桶金"},{"pid":"2fa7fd064072ae0f1d20701d5c47deed9401cb3c","tid":1009221,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaVNE0G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaVNE0G.png&h=81d1cd30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-<br />\n【逄賭必輸︱賭場的莊家優勢】 <br />\n有幾多個人真係喺賭場贏過錢？<br />\n<br />\n會輸係正常嘅！因為賭場有一樣野叫做莊家優勢(House Edge)，即係話玩每一局唔同遊戲，賭場會得到嘅利潤，係用數學方法計算出嚟。而每個遊戲都會有唔同嘅莊家優勢。<br />\n<br />\n例如買大細嘅賭場優勢係2.78%-33.33%（買單雙或圍骰有不同倍率），每局買$1000，賭場就會係你身上獲得$27.8至$333.3嘅利潤，所以你銀包嘅錢只會愈黎愈小，賭場就愈開愈多。<br />\n<br />\n不同遊戲的莊家優勢：<br />\n21點：0.28%起<br />\n百家樂：1.06 - 1.24％<br />\n輪盤：2.70 - 5.26%<br />\n老虎機：2%-15%<br />\n買大細：2.78%-33.33%<br />\n加勒比海撲克：5.22%<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔排除你有一賭就贏嘅機會，只係機會真係好微。難怪有句說話叫「賭錢，等於倒錢落海」啦。<br />\n<br />\n資源來源：Wizard of odds<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nartwork credit: designed by Freepik"},{"pid":"0638ff1204b3e13e449d090c45ed0d7cd109ab9a","tid":1009221,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92f688e2caaf6c1f7eaece4be1b80d4bfc0ebf61","tid":1009221,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"你都on 本多終勝"},{"pid":"9e594338c1d51478ebe994a24591fd1e0160c1da","tid":1009221,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"賭場點都贏你2.8 ％"}]}